title: New build failure on upstream GCC for --target=powerpc-ibm-aix7.{1,2}
body:
On upstream GCC master, I see new errors for the `powerpc-ibm-aix7.1` and `powerpc-ibm-aix7.2` targets starting with the e66fec8e6ba35edf01f86c2bf6514109aba4ded2 commit (gccrs: const folding port):

```shell
.../configure --enable-werror-always --enable-languages=all --disable-gcov --disable-shared --disable-threads --target=powerpc-ibm-aix7.1 --without-headers
[...]
make V=1 all-gcc
[...]
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:32] /usr/lib/gcc-snapshot/bin/g++  -fno-PIE -c  -DIN_GCC_FRONTEND -g -O2   -DIN_GCC  -DCROSS_DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE   -fno-exceptions -fno-rtti -fasynchronous-unwind-tables -W -Wall -Wno-narrowing -Wwrite-strings -Wcast-qual -Wmissing-format-attribute -Wconditionally-supported -Woverloaded-virtual -pedantic -Wno-long-long -Wno-variadic-macros -Wno-overlength-strings -Werror -Wno-unused-parameter -fno-common  -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -I. -Irust -I../../gcc/gcc -I../../gcc/gcc/rust -I../../gcc/gcc/../include  -I../../gcc/gcc/../libcpp/include -I../../gcc/gcc/../libcody  -I../../gcc/gcc/../libdecnumber -I../../gcc/gcc/../libdecnumber/dpd -I../libdecnumber -I../../gcc/gcc/../libbacktrace   -o rust/rust-tree.o -MT rust/rust-tree.o -MMD -MP -MF rust/.deps/rust-tree.TPo -g -O2   -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/lex -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/parse -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/ast -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/analysis -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/expand -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/hir/tree -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/hir -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/resolve -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/util -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/typecheck -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/checks/lints -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/checks/errors -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/checks/errors/privacy -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/util -I ../../gcc/gcc/rust/metadata ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] In file included from ./tm.h:22,
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]                  from ../../gcc/gcc/target.h:52,
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]                  from ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc:34:
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc: In function 'void Rust::mark_exp_read(tree)':
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/config/rs6000/xcoff.h:206:30: error: 'rs6000_xcoff_strip_dollar' was not declared in this scope
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]   206 |   sprintf (LABEL, "*%s..%u", rs6000_xcoff_strip_dollar (PREFIX), (unsigned) (NUM))
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]       |                              ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc:53:3: note: in expansion of macro 'ASM_GENERATE_INTERNAL_LABEL'
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]    53 |   ASM_GENERATE_INTERNAL_LABEL (tmp_name, "Lsrc_loc", 1);
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]       |   ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc: In function 'tree_node* Rust::fold_builtin_source_location(location_t)':
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/config/rs6000/xcoff.h:206:30: error: 'rs6000_xcoff_strip_dollar' was not declared in this scope
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]   206 |   sprintf (LABEL, "*%s..%u", rs6000_xcoff_strip_dollar (PREFIX), (unsigned) (NUM))
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]       |                              ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36] ../../gcc/gcc/rust/backend/rust-tree.cc:4818:7: note: in expansion of macro 'ASM_GENERATE_INTERNAL_LABEL'
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]  4818 |       ASM_GENERATE_INTERNAL_LABEL (tmp_name, "Lsrc_loc", source_location_id++);
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:36]       |       ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[all 2023-02-01 22:06:39] make[1]: *** [../../gcc/gcc/rust/Make-lang.in:367: rust/rust-tree.o] Error 1
```
